{"tid":1364145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【四校聯署】召喚所有喇沙仔、華仁仔、St Marians、Franciscans","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:15:10.000Z","uid":61277,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbea7a55c244095cfade7fec6413217d80c19bb","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"【逆權運動】「送中四人組」母校師生校友聯署 促問責下台：與民為敵失管治認受性<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190725/large/1564046946_31ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190725%2Flarge%2F1564046946_31ce.jpg&h=8ad92c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起：李家超、林鄭月娥、盧偉聰及鄭若驊母校的校友聯署，促問責下台。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反送中浪潮持續，特首林鄭月娥、律政司司長鄭若驊、保安局局長李家超及警務處處長盧偉聰4位高官的中學母校校友，發起四校校友、師生聯署聲明，現正收集簽名及眾籌登報。聲明嚴厲譴責4名校友，要求瀆職官員問責下台，並立即成立獨立調查委員會。4間學校分別為林鄭母校嘉諾撒聖方濟各書院、鄭若驊母校嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院、李家超母校九龍華仁書院及盧偉聰母校喇沙書院。<br />\n<br />\n聯校校友聲明強烈譴責政府在推行《逃犯條例》修訂及處理相關示威活動中，各種背棄民意、倒行逆施、濫用制度暴力、濫用公權力、罔顧市民安危所為，包括以不公議會優勢來強硬推行《逃犯條例》，無視百萬市民上街表達的意見、一度意圖繼續強推修訂，至今仍不肯撤回。此外，政府迅速將6月12日警民衝突定性為「暴動」，其後高官對此砌詞否認、言詞不一，誠信蕩然無存。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又批評警暴問題，指在多次警民衝突中，皆有警員濫用暴力對付示威者，執行職務時慣性以各種方式隱藏身份，更涉嫌選擇性對示威者從嚴執法，而縱容各區襲擊市民的暴徒。聲明特別提到在7月21日，警方動用大量警力武力對付示威者，同時卻消極處理甚至縱容暴徒於元朗襲擊市民，形容「特區政府如此與民為敵，已喪失管治認受性及誠信」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，四位校友作為問責官員，從未實質回應市民五大訴求，導致民間怨氣升級、社會撕裂，顯然失職，對四人所為痛心疾首，要求問責下台。聲明強烈要求政府立即撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，成立獨立調查委員會公正調查。<br />\n<br />\n聯署發起人已經啟動眾籌，目標籌集20萬元，截至今日下午約5時，已籌得接近68,000元，發起人將按最終籌得款項，計劃在本地報章、網媒等刊登聲明；如眾籌有餘款，將全數捐予「612人道支援基金」。<br />\n<br />\n聯校校友聯署網址： <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeLQfq3_KFwC-SiEWkkLnyzrpVcgAHwAeDGDVXK9mCjGa6bxw/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2XHAH-Iht1h_mujowBqjEokqlPiKaWwak2wHGOe23TixZZwPT-OIlU8aM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeLQfq3_KFwC-SiEWkkLnyzrpVcgAHwAeDGDVXK9mCjGa6bxw%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2XHAH-Iht1h_mujowBqjEokqlPiKaWwak2wHGOe23TixZZwPT-OIlU8aM&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=2b9910d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeLQfq3_KFwC-SiEWkkLnyzrpVcgAHwAeDGDVXK9mCjGa6bxw/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2XHAH-Iht1h_mujowBqjEokqlPiKaWwak2wHGOe23TixZZwPT-OIlU8aM</a><br />\n眾籌捐款網址：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%A0%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E%2F&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=81c477cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%A0%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E/</a>"},{"pid":"b1a56721b6114f7dd3a21c10732c438100966011","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"聯校校友聲明<br />\n【截至7月26日下午4時前的聯署人姓名會刊登於報章廣告上，報章廣告截稿過後仍然歡迎繼續聯署，所有眾籌餘款將會全數捐予「612人道支援基金」】<br />\n我們目標為眾籌$200,000，並按最終籌得款項，在下列媒體刊登廣告：<br />\n．本地報章：我們計劃在一至兩份報章刊登廣告；<br />\n．網上媒體：我們計劃在兩、三個網媒刊登廣告，同時讓數個網媒轉載這份聲明；<br />\n．我們更會將這份聲明發送給各大媒體，爭取他們轉載聲明，並通過其他媒體，擴大這把聲音的力量。<br />\n<br />\n廣告費用眾籌安排：<br />\n．眾籌捐款網址：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/聯校聯署聲明/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E8%81%AF%E6%A0%A1%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%2F&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6VmNgp3wQ%2BT5fJEe%2BG4C8OY%3D&h=0086c1aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/聯校聯署聲明/</a><br />\n．⚠️ 大家請記得：在7月26日下午4時之前，請及時聯署，並捐款支持廣告費用，你的姓名就會被包括在報章廣告之中。<br />\n．如果不參與登報聯署的朋友們，也歡迎捐款支持廣告費用。<br />\n．所籌得款項在扣除眾籌網站收費與廣告費用後，如有餘款，將全數撥捐「612人道支援基金」。<br />\n．如有問題，請電郵至 collectivevoice@protonmail.com。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥、鄭若驊、李家超及盧偉聰<br />\n母校教職員、舊生及學生之<br />\n聯署聲明<br />\n<br />\n=================<br />\n嚴厲譴責四名校友<br />\n瀆職官員問責下台<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n=================<br />\n<br />\n我們是來自嘉諾撒聖方濟各書院、嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院、九龍華仁書院和喇沙書院的教職員、舊生及學生*，關注到特區政府於推行《逃犯條例》修訂及處理相關示威活動中各種背棄民意、倒行逆施、濫用制度暴力、濫用公權力、罔顧市民安危的所為，包括：<br />\n<br />\n－ 罔顧議事規則、程序公義，以制度暴力、不公議會優勢來強硬推行《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n－ 無視百萬市民上街表達的意見，一度意圖繼續強硬推行修訂，至今仍不肯撤回<br />\n－ 迅速將6月12日的警民衝突定性為「暴動」，其後各高官對此砌詞否認、言詞不一，誠信蕩然無存<br />\n－ 於多次警民衝突中有警員濫用暴力對付示威者<br />\n－ 警員於執行職務時慣性以各種方式隱藏身份，顯然為逃避違法責任<br />\n－ 選擇性對示威者從嚴執法，而縱容各區襲擊市民的暴徒<br />\n－ 於7月21日，動用大量警力武力對付示威者，同時卻消極處理甚至縱容暴徒於元朗襲擊市民<br />\n<br />\n特區政府如此與民為敵，已喪失管治認受性及誠信。四位校友作為問責官員，從未實質回應市民五大訴求，導致民間怨氣升級、社會撕裂，顯然失職。我等對四位校友的所為痛心疾首，予以嚴厲譴責，四位校友必須問責下台。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，我們強烈要求特區政府立即撤回修訂，並成立獨立調查委員會，公正調查特區政府自推出《逃犯條例》修訂以來的失誤及警方濫權、濫暴及警黑合作等指控，以彰顯公義，讓社會重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n* 此聲明由校友自發聯署，並不代表嘉諾撒聖方濟各書院、嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院、九龍華仁書院和喇沙書院與各校舊生會"},{"pid":"e09951a6ceb3e8ee2bad8cc7af4aab5106ce59de","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d792e26aa2acb5377d074ef415087d8d063bd163","tid":1364145,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"大力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05ba57a66eb632db53a8844b22c159f8ad7b9b7","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03011f08114738383627cb6a0d0c2b82a7ca91d","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ece955a70476a5138c360f2439c14d2c51b4b36","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5efda5550205848eb5da9f41e5b940e1bdf10f1","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffeefc5ed8d539c710c1be2bac152c55a4ff766","tid":1364145,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:13:28.000Z","msg":"呢四間學校既巴絲打去曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489bfef81a1db96dcc1543ee10aaef8c1a957fd8","tid":1364145,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"7c64ed1abe6d4375a92bf68254ef8b8019c6608e","tid":1364145,"uid":8389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"舊生幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fce5185e6c2ecbc5d5b2c935e0edd3cb487b91","tid":1364145,"uid":25160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  錢已交"},{"pid":"53f9a1756748c5775603da8b7f6adb6547054e70","tid":1364145,"uid":273437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:26: